{"tid":2214970,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：承認修訂「傳媒代表」定義政治責任 香港民族反應巨大證擊中要害","createTime":"2020-09-23T15:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T16:53:34.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b9769ed7bee10c4be720083c8f48a11bbf587c51","tid":2214970,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:36:05.000Z","msg":"外交部駐港公署要求外國記者會 停插手香港事務<br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港特派員公署，透過微信公眾號，就香港外國記者會反對警方修訂&ldquo;傳媒代表&rdquo;定義，表示強烈不滿和堅決反對，要求外國記者會立即停止打著新聞自由幌子，插手香港事務。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指，去年&ldquo;修例風波&rdquo;中，一些反中亂港分子以記者之名，公然阻礙警方執法，甚至襲擊警員，嚴重破壞香港法治與社會秩序，外國記者會急不可耐，跳出來公然為&ldquo;假記者真暴徒&rdquo;美化洗白，實質就是妄圖包庇縱容&ldquo;黑暴&rdquo;&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;勢力亂港罪行，唯恐香港不亂，用心險惡，敦促外國記者會遵守中國和香港特區法律法規，停止蓄意製造、挑動事端。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2358617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2358617&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9ooeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=fc5534db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2358617</a>"},{"pid":"7edffa1b4824db501956387c73b9a909416de8fe","tid":2214970,"uid":289978,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:46:39.000Z","msg":"邊個會唔對非法政權反應大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美國射忍者飛彈發動斬首行動唔通又係因為俾人擊中要害?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那蝗on撚9邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc30f6ab2b89f2c17fdda9de7bdfaa1d8d8aefe","tid":2214970,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375aa5563271187c2839844dc56ccb88e9887f95","tid":2214970,"uid":194005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim